  <brief_title>The Efficacy and Safety of PRC-063 in Adult ADHD Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase III, Randomized, Double-Blind, Placebo-Controlled, Parallel-Arm, Multi-Center Study Measuring the Efficacy and Safety of PRC-063 in Adult ADHD Patients</official_title>
